{"parents": [], "prev": {"link": "../analytics/reference/", "title": "Reference"}, "next": {"link": "guides/emails/design_email/", "title": "Designing an Email"}, "title": "Automation", "meta": null, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"automation\">\n<h1>Automation<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#automation\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<p>The automation app lets users craft custom workflows for users that automate\nsome portion of the user\u2019s journey. Triggered by some external action (e.g.\nresponding to a form, clicking a link in an email, etc), users are enrolled in\na workflow and then passed through a series of steps that either alter their\ncustomer record or send some sort of communication.</p>\n<div class=\"toctree-wrapper compound\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/design_email/\">Designing an Email</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_text_block/\">Text Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_divider_block/\">Divider Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_image_block/\">Image Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_button_block/\">Button Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_preference_block/\">Preferences Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_social_share_block/\">Social Share Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_social_follow_block/\">Social Follow Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_video_block/\">Video Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_web_version_block/\">Web Version Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_performance/\">Email Performance</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/emails/\">Emails</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/workflows/ask_question_block/\">Ask Question Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/workflows/create_a_workflow/\">Creating a Workflow via Automation</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/workflows/design_a_workflow/\">Designing a Workflow</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/workflows/dial_by_extension_block/\">Dial by Extension Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/workflows/dial_by_name_block/\">Dial by Name Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/workflows/dial_menu_block/\">Dial Menu Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/workflows/enroll_in_a_workflow_block/\">Enroll in Workflow Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/workflows/forward_call_block/\">Forward Call Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/workflows/go_to_menu_block/\">Goto Menu Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/workflows/if_then_block/\">If/Then Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/workflows/new_workflow/\">Creating a New Workflow</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/workflows/play_recording_block/\">Play Recording Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/workflows/play_recording_microp